msgid ""
"Learn the Klein for Ray execution model, DataStream abstraction, keyed "
"state, event time, and checkpoint recovery."
msgstr "了解 Klein for Ray 的执行模型、DataStream 抽象、键控状态、事件时间和检查点恢复。"

msgid "Key concepts"
msgstr "核心概念"

msgid ""
"Klein for Ray represents a pipeline as a lazy dataflow graph. Sources "
"produce records, transformations create new streams, partitioners route "
"data, and sinks trigger execution."
msgstr "Klein for Ray 将管道表示为惰性数据流图。源生成记录，转换创建新数据流，分区器路由数据，而 sink 触发执行。"

msgid ""
"![A Klein DataStream pipeline running on Ray](_static/key-concepts-"
"pipeline.png)"
msgstr "![在 Ray 上运行的 Klein DataStream 管道](_static/key-concepts-pipeline.png)"

msgid "A Klein DataStream pipeline running on Ray"
msgstr "在 Ray 上运行的 Klein DataStream 管道"

msgid ""
"The solid path is the record flow. Partitioning determines which physical"
" task receives each record. Watermarks and checkpoint barriers use the "
"same ordered edges, so they describe all records that precede them. The "
"[architecture guide](architecture.md) expands this logical view into "
"planning, control-plane, data-plane, and recovery components."
msgstr ""
"实线路径表示记录流。分区决定由哪个物理任务接收每条记录。水位线和检查点屏障使用相同的有序边，因此它们描述了位于其之前的所有记录。[架构指南](architecture.md)"
" 将这一逻辑视图展开为规划、控制平面、数据平面和恢复组件。"

msgid "What is a DataStream?"
msgstr "什么是 DataStream？"

msgid ""
"A `DataStream` is a logical collection of records and the operations "
"needed to produce them. Methods such as `map()`, `filter()`, `key_by()`, "
"and `join()` add operators to the graph. They don't run work when you "
"call them."
msgstr ""
"`DataStream` 是记录以及生成这些记录所需操作的逻辑集合。`map()`、`filter()`、`key_by()` 和 "
"`join()` 等方法会向图中添加算子；调用这些方法时并不会立即执行工作。"

msgid ""
"A stream belongs to one internal pipeline owner. Module-level `ray.klein`"
" functions hide that bookkeeping, matching Ray Data's source-construction"
" style. Direct `KleinContext` construction is an advanced escape hatch "
"for a process that must build isolated pipelines."
msgstr ""
"数据流归属于一个内部管道所有者。模块级 `ray.klein` 函数会隐藏这些记账细节，其风格与 Ray Data "
"的源构建方式一致。对于必须构建隔离管道的进程，直接构造 `KleinContext` 是一种高级逃生口。"

msgid "How does Klein choose an execution mode?"
msgstr "Klein 如何选择执行模式？"

msgid "In `auto` mode, Klein selects one execution mode for the whole graph:"
msgstr "在 `auto` 模式下，Klein 为整个计算图选择一种执行模式："

msgid ""
"An unbounded source, any graph vertex without a batch lowering, or `udf"
".ignore-exception=true` selects streaming execution. Klein deploys long-"
"lived source, transform, and sink tasks on Ray. The exception policy "
"needs Klein's record-level error handling and metric semantics."
msgstr ""
"存在无界数据源、任一计算图顶点没有批处理下沉实现，或设置 `udf.ignore-exception=true`，都会选择原生流处理执行。Klein 会在 Ray "
"上部署长生命周期的数据源、转换和 sink 任务。该异常策略依赖 Klein 的记录级错误处理和指标语义。"

msgid ""
"Only a fully batch-lowerable, bounded graph selects batch and becomes "
"lazy Ray Data `Dataset` operations."
msgstr "只有所有数据源均有界且整个图都可下沉为批处理时，才会选择批处理，并将其转换为惰性的 Ray Data `Dataset` 操作。"

msgid ""
"You can override detection through `execution.runtime.mode`. A graph must"
" use operations supported by its selected mode. A bounded custom "
"`SourceFunction` without a batch lowering, or a graph with a streaming-"
"only intermediate operator, therefore selects streaming automatically; "
"forcing batch fails."
msgstr ""
"可以通过 `execution.runtime.mode` 覆盖自动检测。计算图必须只使用所选模式支持的操作。因此，缺少批处理下沉实现的有界自定义"
" `SourceFunction`，或包含仅支持流处理的中间算子的计算图，都会自动选择流处理；强制使用批处理将失败。"

msgid "How does data move through a streaming graph?"
msgstr "数据如何在流式图中移动？"

msgid ""
"Streaming tasks exchange ordered micro-batches. A partitioner chooses the"
" downstream task for each batch or record. Control messages, including "
"checkpoint barriers and event-time progress, use the same physical edges "
"and flush preceding data first. This ordering prevents a barrier or "
"watermark from overtaking earlier records."
msgstr "流式任务交换有序微批。分区器为每个批次或每条记录选择下游任务。检查点屏障和事件时间进度等控制消息使用相同的物理边，并会先刷新位于其之前的数据。这种顺序可防止屏障或水位线越过更早的记录。"

msgid ""
"Backpressure limits in-flight data between tasks. Ray actors provide task"
" isolation and scheduling, while the Ray Object Store carries shared "
"immutable values such as large checkpoint fragments."
msgstr "背压限制任务之间的在途数据。Ray actor 提供任务隔离和调度，Ray Object Store 则承载大型检查点片段等共享不可变值。"

msgid "What is keyed state?"
msgstr "什么是键控状态？"

msgid ""
"`key_by()` partitions records by a stable key and returns a "
"`KeyedStream`. Stateful operators access `ValueState`, `ListState`, and "
"`MapState` through descriptors. State descriptors can define time-to-live"
" (TTL) behavior, and stateful functions can register processing-time or "
"event-time timers."
msgstr ""
"`key_by()` 按稳定键对记录分区，并返回 `KeyedStream`。有状态算子通过描述符访问 "
"`ValueState`、`ListState` 和 `MapState`。状态描述符可以定义生存时间 (TTL) "
"行为，有状态函数还可以注册处理时间或事件时间定时器。"

msgid ""
"Klein maps each key to a fixed key group. A task owns a contiguous range "
"of key groups, so a restored job can change operator parallelism without "
"rehashing its keys. The checkpoint stores state, TTL indexes, and timers "
"by key group. `state.keyed.max-parallelism` defines the key-group space "
"and is part of checkpoint compatibility."
msgstr ""
"Klein "
"将每个键映射到固定的键组。一个任务拥有一段连续的键组范围，因此恢复后的作业可以调整算子并行度，而无需重新哈希键。检查点按键组存储状态、TTL "
"索引和定时器。`state.keyed.max-parallelism` 定义键组空间，并且是检查点兼容性的一部分。"

msgid ""
"See [Managed state](ray-native-state.md) for backend selection, "
"rescaling, and timer behavior."
msgstr "有关后端选择、扩缩容和定时器行为，请参阅[托管状态](ray-native-state.md)。"

msgid "What is event time?"
msgstr "什么是事件时间？"

msgid ""
"Event time comes from timestamps in the records rather than the clock on "
"a worker. A `Watermark(t)` states that one input doesn't expect another "
"event at or before timestamp `t`. A multi-input operator advances to the "
"minimum watermark across its active inputs."
msgstr ""
"事件时间来自记录中的时间戳，而不是 worker 上的时钟。`Watermark(t)` 表示某个输入不再预期收到时间戳小于或等于 `t` "
"的事件。多输入算子会推进到所有活动输入中的最小水位线。"

msgid ""
"An input that has not emitted its first watermark blocks progress. An "
"idle input doesn't block progress. When data resumes, the input becomes "
"active before the new record enters the operator. This protocol keeps "
"windows and joins moving when a Kafka partition or another physical input"
" has no data."
msgstr ""
"尚未发出第一个水位线的输入会阻塞进度，空闲输入则不会。数据恢复时，该输入会在新记录进入算子前重新变为活动状态。当 Kafka "
"分区或其他物理输入没有数据时，此协议仍能让窗口和连接继续推进。"

msgid ""
"See [Event time and idle inputs](event-time.md) for watermark strategies "
"and source connector hooks."
msgstr "有关水位线策略和源连接器钩子，请参阅[事件时间与空闲输入](event-time.md)。"

msgid "How do checkpoints recover a job?"
msgstr "检查点如何恢复作业？"

msgid ""
"A checkpoint barrier separates records before and after a consistent "
"state snapshot. Stateful tasks export immutable key-group fragments. "
"Small snapshots remain inline, while large snapshots can use the Ray "
"Object Store as a hot recovery cache. Completed checkpoints are persisted"
" to a filesystem or object store for recovery after a cluster or "
"coordinator loss."
msgstr ""
"检查点屏障将一致状态快照前后的记录分隔开。有状态任务会导出不可变键组片段。小型快照保持内联，大型快照则可使用 Ray Object Store "
"作为热恢复缓存。已完成的检查点会持久化到文件系统或对象存储，以便在集群或协调器丢失后恢复。"

msgid ""
"Klein publishes checkpoint metadata only after every referenced state "
"object is durable and verified. Recovery ignores incomplete checkpoint "
"directories. See [Durable checkpoint storage](checkpoint-storage.md) for "
"the directory layout and publication protocol."
msgstr ""
"只有在所有被引用的状态对象均已持久化并通过验证后，Klein "
"才会发布检查点元数据。恢复过程会忽略不完整的检查点目录。有关目录布局和发布协议，请参阅[持久检查点存储](checkpoint-"
"storage.md)。"

msgid ""
"Klein provides at-least-once progress semantics. A non-transactional sink"
" can observe replayed records after recovery. Managed state and "
"checkpoints don't turn an arbitrary sink into an exactly-once sink."
msgstr "Klein 提供至少一次进度语义。恢复后，非事务型 sink 可能观察到重放记录。托管状态和检查点不会让任意 sink 自动具备精确一次语义。"

msgid "How does Klein relate to Ray Data?"
msgstr "Klein 与 Ray Data 有何关系？"

msgid ""
"Klein doesn't copy Ray Data reader or `Dataset` method signatures. "
"`ray.klein.read_csv`, `read_parquet`, and other bounded readers resolve "
"their installed `ray.data` functions dynamically. `stream.data` exposes "
"compatible Dataset operations."
msgstr ""
"Klein 不会复制 Ray Data reader 或 `Dataset` "
"方法签名。`ray.klein.read_csv`、`read_parquet` 及其他有界 reader 会动态解析已安装的 "
"`ray.data` 函数。`stream.data` 公开兼容的 Dataset 操作。"

msgid ""
"Use native `DataStream` methods for streaming semantics. Use "
"`stream.data` when the operation is a bounded Ray Data operation. See "
"[Ray Data interoperability](ray-data-interop.md) for details and the "
"[connector catalog](connectors/index.md) for each connector's supported "
"mode and guarantees."
msgstr ""
"需要流式语义时，请使用原生 `DataStream` 方法；操作属于有界 Ray Data 操作时，请使用 `stream.data`。详情请参阅"
" [Ray Data 互操作性](ray-data-"
"interop.md)，各连接器支持的模式和保证则参见[连接器目录](connectors/index.md)。"

